BP Removal Detection — all actions in order:
Action 1: Select (Data Operations)

From — fx: body('Read_BP_Excel')?['value']
Switch to text mode
Map — fx: item()?['Business Process ID']
Rename to: Extract BP IDs From Excel

Action 2: Dataverse → List rows

Table: Parent Business Processes
Filter rows — fx: 'pei_emslifecyclestatus eq 890920000'
Rename to: List Active BPs

Action 3: Apply to each

Select output — fx: outputs('List_Active_BPs')?['body/value']
Rename to: Check BP Removals

Inside Check BP Removals:
Action 4: Condition

Left — fx: contains(body('Extract_BP_IDs_From_Excel'), items('Check_BP_Removals')?['pei_businessprocessidentifier'])
Operator: is equal to
Right — fx: false
Rename to: BP Not In File

Inside BP Not In File → If Yes:
Action 5: Dataverse → Update a row

Table: Parent Business Processes
Row ID — fx: items('Check_BP_Removals')?['pei_parentbusinessprocessid']
EMS Lifecycle Status: pick Removed from dropdown
Rename to: Mark BP Removed

Action 6: Increment variable

Name: varBPRemoved
Value: 1
